01:52.000 --> 02:04.000
For three and a half decades this tyrant dispatched terrorism across the world, made his own people miserable and worked constantly and tirelessly on a program to annihilate the state of Israel.

02:05.000 --> 02:11.000
That plan is there no longer and there are many signs that this tyrant is also no longer.

