Yeah he announced that on histruth social media site and when he said that Ayatollah Khomeini had been killed he described him as one of the most evil people in history.

07:01.000 --> 07:06.000
And then went on to say this is now the single greatest chance for Iranians to take back their country.

07:06.000 --> 07:18.000
And he's also been talking on the phone to a number of American journalists describing the operation so far as a tremendous success and saying he believes that quite a large proportion of the Iranian leadership have now been killed.

07:21.000 --> 07:29.000
The White House has released photos of President Trump monitoring operations in a specially constructed facility in Mar-a-Lago.

07:29.000 --> 07:34.000
