11:53.000 --> 11:55.000
Is this the war you cheer for?

11:55.000 --> 11:57.000
A mixture of emotions.

11:57.000 --> 12:00.000
For some a fear that more violence is yet to come.

12:00.000 --> 12:05.000
For others a sense that the regime's hold could finally be challenged.

12:05.000 --> 12:10.000
The country is scarred by months of protests and deadly crackdowns on certainty rains.

12:10.000 --> 12:17.000
